Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.24,0:20:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好像成了这家伙的影像教材
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,总之这么一来就大功告成了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.99,0:20:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不过还是留作纪念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.00,0:20:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟是珍贵的出道作品嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.92,0:20:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我来帮你保管
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,有空咱们一起看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我之所以能站在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,都是多亏了你们 我最最可爱的Fans
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.30,0:21:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,大家真的 真的 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这部电影是Panty小姐的出道作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,对对 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.45,0:21:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我货真价实的出道作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.87,0:21:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,同样 对于Stocking小姐来说 也是她的出道作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.16,0:21:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,对 能姐妹共演 简直就像做梦一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.05,0:21:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,最开始我们是想做组合
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.32,0:21:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你也看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.04,0:21:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这孩子看上去很阴沉 就是叫那啥哥特?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.59,0:21:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说和这个作品会不会不太搭调
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.27,0:21:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,于是在和导演还有制片人商讨后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.76,0:21:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,决定由我一个人主演这部电影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.08,0:21:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我想这样的决定大家也会更开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.38,0:21:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,另外有Stocking的镜头
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.07,0:21:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,已经被优秀的CG团队删得干干净净
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.08,0:21:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不留半点痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.42,0:21:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是本片的看点之一
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.52,0:21:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,大家敬请期待
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.84,0:22:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.89,0:22:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你真坏～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.46,0:22:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌～这里还有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.68,0:22:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我是Anarchy Panty
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.68,0:22:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,全世界的好男人都是我的囊中物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.12,0:22:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,P…P…Panty…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.81,0:22:57.33,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Heaven, please sing for me a song of life
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.55,0:23:02.64,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Heaven, take me into your skies
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:07.33,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}There's no place here for me to hide my cries
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.34,0:23:10.27,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Night and day I'm missing you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.27,0:23:14.57,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}You're so close (so close)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:17.97,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}And it's you that I believe in (I believe in)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.97,0:23:22.76,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}So close, but far away so far I can't touch
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.76,0:23:26.81,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}I'll hold on, 'cause it's you I love so dearly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.81,0:23:29.82,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}When the rain, the storm and all is up
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.82,0:23:33.01,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Caress me with your sweet lullaby
